snippet.title: Beers and Boomerangs VR - Official Gameplay Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A game where you throw boomerangs at kangaroos that are trying to steal your beer.
More info at https://beersandboomerangs.com/
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1588610?utm_source=website

Developed with love by a nerd couple.

#BeersAndBoomerangs #VirtualReality #BeersAndBoomerangsVR


Music:
Le Grand Chase by Kevin MacLeod
Link: https://incompetech.filmmusic.io/song/4670-le-grand-chase
